{"tid":1779342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"動向教育中心 diploma in business finance","createTime":"2019-12-11T15:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T16:28:04.000Z","uid":313246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7a7f3755750a525ea14f5979ae7a8ca2f475bc","tid":1779342,"uid":313246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人有報，係咪伏黎架，好像有好多大師教導，我個fd 推介我，又話佢個fd有成功，好像好多成功例子，但係又好像好多差評有冇巴打近排係參加左，有覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"612cd3d5352bda031022a8e0f61826c28b23d72f","tid":1779342,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"傳銷"},{"pid":"ff147f579ebdc6c48aedad7b0d935d8bc95a4a53","tid":1779342,"uid":81253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"八大咁多間唔讀點解要搵不知明教育機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b691ea7155b4ab8779e9fe0e20e9ee0ea4701d4a","tid":1779342,"uid":313246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff147f579ebdc6c48aedad7b0d935d8bc95a4a53","tid":1779342,"uid":81253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"八大咁多間唔讀點解要搵不知明教育機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"你唔會唸到一個識左10年嘅fd會比伏你踩"},{"pid":"24191ed9736d654430f16a4006acaf56ac211ab3","tid":1779342,"uid":318451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"最近有friend都搵我join<br />\n話好多人排隊讀喎<br />\n但真係唔知好唔好讀<br />\n好似比人昆左咁"},{"pid":"18c7d0926585a085aaf7e42b9dfc3de5e775db41","tid":1779342,"uid":349125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24191ed9736d654430f16a4006acaf56ac211ab3","tid":1779342,"uid":318451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"最近有friend都搵我join<br />\n話好多人排隊讀喎<br />\n但真係唔知好唔好讀<br />\n好似比人昆左咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"我都係。 可交流下？"},{"pid":"3bab42db7c71f170